import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1):
    v0 = jnp.maximum(x0, x1)
    v1 = jnp.tanh(v0)
    v2 = jnp.cos(v0)
    v3 = jnp.exp(v0)
    v4 = jnp.subtract(v3, v1)
    v5 = jnp.exp(x0)
    v6 = jnp.subtract(x1, x0)
    v7 = jnp.multiply(v2, v3)
    v8 = jnp.exp(v7)
    v9 = jnp.maximum(v8, v8)
    return v9
